<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-13666] Route autoStartup cancellation from a RoutePolicy is not working properly in Camel 3</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-13666</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like route autoStartup cancellation from a route policy is not working properly with Camel 3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For instance, ClusteredRoutePolicy.onInit() is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/core/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/impl/cluster/ClusteredRoutePolicy.java#L171&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;setting autoStartup to false&lt;/a&gt;,&#160;but routes are actually started.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;How to reproduce:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-jgroups-raft/src/test/java/org/apache/camel/component/jgroups/raft/cluster/JGroupsRaftClusteredRoutePolicyTest.java#L97&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;JGroupsRaftClusteredRoutePolicyTest&lt;/a&gt;&#160;reproduces this issue when autoStartup(false) is not explicitly set in createRouteBuilder.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/core/camel-core/src/test/java/org/apache/camel/impl/RoutePolicyAutoStartupCancelledOnInitTest.java&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;RoutePolicyAutoStartupCancelledOnInitTest&lt;/a&gt; is a small reproducer too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Workaround:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 Explicitly set autoStartup(false):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
from(...).autoStartup(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
